spec_data.Name: perl-HTML-BarGraph
spec_data.Description:
HTML::BarGraph is a module that creates graphics for one or more data-sets,
using plain HTML and, optionally, one-pixel images, which are stretched
using the width and height attributes of the HTML img tag.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:03:16 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generate multiset bar graphs using plain HTML
